## 4. Unbreakable Code Standards

### 4.1 Zero Placeholder Code
Every line must be complete, functional, production-ready code.

### 4.2 Security First
- All user inputs validated **both client-side AND server-side**.
- Eloquent ORM only (no raw SQL except for analytics).
- Path sandboxing: AI Agent writes restricted to `app/`, `resources/views/`, `routes/` only.
- `.env`, `vendor/`, `storage/`, `bootstrap/` are ABSOLUTELY WRITE-PROTECTED from AI Agent.
- Every AI Agent write action logged in `ai_actions_log` (who, when, what file, diff summary).
- Rate limiting on all auth + AI endpoints.
- CSRF protection on all POST/PUT/DELETE routes.
- Strict Policies/Gates for all role-based access.

### 4.3 UI/UX Excellence
- Dark Mode by Default: `#0a0a0a` backgrounds, `#111111` panels, `#161b22` surfaces.
- Glowing accents: Violet (`#8b5cf6`) and Cyan (`#06b6d4`) with `box-shadow` glows.
- Glassmorphism: `backdrop-blur-md bg-white/5 border border-white/10`.
- Ultra-thin custom scrollbars (webkit styling).
- Premium fonts: Inter (UI text), JetBrains Mono (code/terminal).
- All async actions → skeleton loaders.
- All success/error → premium toast notifications.
- Staggered entrance animations on lists.

### 4.4 Stack Adherence
- **Backend:** Laravel 11 (PHP 8.3+) — Controllers, Models, Migrations, Seeders, Policies, Events, Jobs.
- **Database:** MySQL 8.0+ — Proper foreign keys, indexes, column comments.
- **Frontend:** Blade templates + Tailwind CSS (custom config) + Vanilla JS / Alpine.js.
- **Real-time:** Laravel Reverb (WebSockets) + Laravel Echo.
- **Editor:** Monaco Editor (CDN or self-hosted).
- **AI:** Anthropic Claude API (Opus 4 / Sonnet) with tool-use function calling.
- **Video:** Self-hosted Jitsi Meet or JaaS (Jitsi as a Service).

