## 5. Git & Project Hygiene

- Structure code logically: Models in `app/Models/`, Controllers in `app/Http/Controllers/`, Blade views in `resources/views/`.
- Each Phase completion = one logical commit group.
- Use descriptive commit messages: `Phase 2: Workspace IDE — Monaco Editor + Split-Pane Layout`.
- Never commit `.env` file or secrets.

